window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It began with a wishing lantern and a shimmer faerie. </b></p> <p>Thirteen imaginative tales&nbsp;filled with revenge, battles, hope, and gut-punching endings set in Kingfountain, Muirwood, and exciting new settings, from best-selling author Jeff Wheeler.&nbsp;</p> <p>Immerse yourself in worlds with tragic kingdoms and mad kings, magic communication with bees in haunted ruins, a boy who serves the mystical Ravenmaster of Pent Tower, and the secrets of Metamorphistry.</p>"; 
